    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. To make it even more impactful for the students, can you add a section that explains why this concept is considered the most effective way for the judiciary to act as a check on the majority? I want them to see it as a necessary safeguard against the 'tyranny of the majority' when it comes to personal freedoms.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
