      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's really clear. One more thing though—some critics argue that this gives judges way too much power to basically make up new rights that aren't explicitly in the Constitution. How would you address those critics in the lecture so the students understand why their arguments are seen as being less valid than the protection of these fundamental liberties?",
